  <!-- Wilayah Explanation -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-6 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-4">🕋 What is Wilayah?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-200">
      <strong>Wilayah</strong> in Shia Islam refers to the divine guardianship and spiritual leadership granted by Allah to the Prophet and the Imams. Imam Ali (AS) was the first Wali appointed after the Prophet’s death at Ghadir Khumm.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
      It's not just political leadership, but includes guiding people in faith, knowledge, and divine authority.
    </p>
  </section>

